result.title: 2006 - 2008 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Irish Sea Fish Egg Production Survey - Zooplankton Data
result.name: 2006-2008-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-irish-sea-fish-egg-product
result.notes:
A series of cruises carried out in the Irish Sea from 2006 to 2008 by the 
Centre for Environment, Fisheries and Aquaculture Science. This data consists 
of the analysis results of the fine mesh (PUP) net samples and consist of 
numbers of zooplankton identified, along with associated positional data and 
volumes filtered.
